{"tid":1502883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想贏，就要攬炒，想攬炒就要迫中共出解放軍","createTime":"2019-08-24T18:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T17:55:01.000Z","uid":74090,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e8538500cc6fa0dcd605fc2dab936e93783682","tid":1502883,"uid":74090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:11:57.000Z","msg":"抗爭左兩個月，而家全個抗爭已經定型左響5大訴求<br />\n但大家應該感覺到，到今日依然未有成效<br />\n既然係咁，不如再將目標推大啲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">迫共匪出解放軍攬炒</span></span><br />\n唔係聽日就開始，但正如大家所講，每件事都要有死線<br />\n與其苟延殘喘，不如直接將目標放去攬炒<br />\n迫共匪出解放軍，只要出解放軍鎮壓香港<br />\n就可以直接令全球各國共同制裁共匪，用全世界力量攻擊共匪<br />\n勢要整個共匪政權崩潰，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港先可以真正火鳳凰重生</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bwgh56E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwgh56E.jpg&h=36bf330f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"988c1ba810da4915b99fd11863d8a189994b67a5","tid":1502883,"uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:12:48.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fb3a29ff43df10ca0457ff65ac1104ec2c43976e","tid":1502883,"uid":73972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:18:50.000Z","msg":"大陸話出解放軍擺明靠嚇，佢地一定唔會出，香港班黑警要鎮壓班示威者其實綽綽有餘"},{"pid":"27e5f0495d8f0903c272d7dec1781ddccdd1e69f","tid":1502883,"uid":69212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:25:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28b4762781edf8cee185443c931b4e147fadd689","tid":1502883,"uid":74090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:29:44.000Z","msg":"只有攬炒，先可以解決樓價問題<br />\n將班為富不仁仆街拉落馬<br />\n比真普選更加撤底去解決香港長年累月嘅問題根源"},{"pid":"22b72089320f38b2fbb4bb6d75aa11bcf732c8cd","tid":1502883,"uid":74090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":